OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian army officer: Our  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftroops tortured Ukrainians 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Allegations of brutal interrogations,  
OL,6, where Ukrainian men were shot and      
OL,7, threatened with rape, have been made by
OL,8, a former Russian military officer.     
OL,10,FKonstantin Yefremov, the most senior   
OL,11,Fofficer to speak openly, told the BBC  
OL,12,Fin an exclusive interview Russia now   
OL,13,Fsees him as a traitor and defector.    
OL,15,FAt one site in southern Ukraine, he    
OL,16,Fsaid "the interrogations, the torture, 
OL,17,Fcontinued for about a week".           
OL,19,F"Every day, at night, sometimes twice a
OL,20,Fday."                                  
